lines: To pakuru Ruoth me polo malo;

Gi nam, kodi yien, gi gode kod lum;
Gik moko me piny onyisowa ma,

To gik moko duto mag piny

Wang'i mang'uon miya bedo gi ler,
An kenda ka, to tienda ol e yo,

Ji duto pake e piny ka;
nakwan gik mag piny ka nono;

title: Ka ma Yesu Chon Notho E Yath

lines: Kama Yesu chon notho e yath,

To morna ok norum kasomo wachni;

Mond' abed gi Yesu gi malaika.
Ruoth Yesu, Jawarwa, In e ngimana;
In morna, warruokna, In kar yueyona;
Onge ng'a machalo kod Yesu Jawar;
Napake, nadende kod wende mag chuny;

E wuodha duto me piny ka,
E wuodha duto me piny ka,
Ok alem ne mor mar pinyni,
Na ti gi mor kat e chandruok,
Na ti gi mor kat e chandruok,

title: To En Ng'a Man E Kund Dhok

Kata mudho olil manade, osesingo nobed buta
Omiya ler marieny e mudho, Kendo ber e kar richo.

Awero hera mar  Jawarna manotho e yath ni an,

Omiya ler marieny  e mudho, kendo ber e kar richo.

Wadwaro lami, ka wan nyimi ka,

ka nahulo kak' ageni, In Jawarna;

E, awuoro kaka nowarowa, kaka nowarowa;

Mond' ayud yueyo gi kuwe man kuomi.

Mond' ayud yueyo gi kuwe man kuomi.

Chunya mor kaweyo richo gi keth,

title: Kristo Obedo Misango Mar Golo Richo

lines: Ne en ku mabor ma onge jakwath.
Komanyo e thim mak ojok ngang',
Ne en ka malich, kodwaro tho.
Ma yandi olal e thim ku mabor."
Dwe to orieny kuom chikne to,
En gweth manade, en kuwe manade,
En yo maber madhiyo kar ngima
Ruoth nobed koda ndalo duto te,
Ler wang' chieng' orieny e gode,
To ler moloyo ler wang' chieng'
Kuom kit wuodha e piny ka.
Mond' abed e tiend Ruoth Yesu,
To ji mang'eny pok ong'eyo (ong'eyo) Herani modhiero;
To ji mang'eny pok ong'enyo (ong'eyo) Rembi moseluoka (oluoka).
Ang'eyo Intie buta, Ruoth, Moloyo ji me piny;
Kaparoi ayudo mor Moloyona mor piny.
Iketo morni e chunya, Ma piny ok nyal golo;
Da ok abed gi herani, Kuyo dipong' chunya.
Kwayudo mor e ngimawa Kwawuotho kodi ka,
To wanayud mor manade Kwaneni Wang' gi Wang'.
Yesu e berna bende e lerna;
Ka tichne rumo, ka piny ogik,
Kuom yie, gi geno, gi paro,
Weche Nyasaye gin ler mar piny,
E ndalo maduong' ka chandruok biro
Ka yembe kudho ka apaka lich
Motwe e loch ma ok nyal yiengni
Ka apaka ger ka yembe kudho
Ok onyal pudhre kata e kar tho
Kat' apaka ng'eny pod nochung' matek
Ka wanane ler ka piny yawore
Rangeye mag lulu ka rieny maler
Ka chandruok kadho ma nyaka chieng'.
Mond' atim rito ka jalok ji;
Kata ni mond' aidh loka got,
Ni mond' achik yo makiya; Nawachi,
Dobed mich ma ok dak nyal rom;
Tiuru, tiuru, wan jotich mag Nyasaye;
Watimgi gi teko duto te ma wan go.
Gi pi ngima ni jo ma riyo oloyo;
Msalaba gi bendechwa mond' orieny ni ji,
Mondo pinyruodh mudho koro orum chutho;
To pinyruoth mar Kristo omedre kendo rieny.
Tiuru, tiuri, kuom teko mar Ruodhwa;
Eka chieng' giko wanayud osimb ngima.
Jo maler ginirieny kaka chieng' godiechieng',

title: Wan Wamor Kwatiyo Ni Ruoth Yesu

lines: Wan wamor kwatiyo ni Ruoth Yesu;
Wan wawuok ka chunywa yie timo
Watiyo gi mor, watiyo gi mor;
Wanamor mar nyiso ji wach kuome,
Kak' ohero ji duto e piny;
Kristo, mobedo e duong' mar Wuoro,
Jokeyo ni kanye mondo tim tich
Mar kayo cham maber e piny marach?
Pand keyo en adier mar Wach Nyasaye,
To yueyo onge nyaka tich rumo.
Ni mond' oriwre e tich maber ni Ruoth?
Mar kayo cham maber e puoth Ruoth?
Cham maber nitie kata buya ng'eny;
To chokuru duto e mor mar Ruoth.
Puothe koro chiek kwonde duto te;
To jokeyo nok, kendo tich duong' ngang';
Eka unudonji e mor mar Ruoth.

title: E Dho Wath Man Loka Nam

lines: E dho wath man loka nam;
To Yesu nolor gi duong' mare,
(En malo e polo kosayo ni ji!).
Yie ichiwri ne sani In bende nine ng'wono mare,

title: Nitie Luong Mobiro E Wi Apaka

lines: Nitie chuny mi konyo gi chuny miwaro
Kow ler --- Injili mogwedhi Mondo orieny --- kuonde duto,
Kow ler --- mondo lerni orieny Omeny piny --- manyaka chieng'.
Walem ni gweth oumwa kwonde duto
Kik wajony mar lando tich mar herane,
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye, gokinyi ka pod wang' chieng' nitie?
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye, owadwa e saa ma chieng' rieny makech.
Kendo tich keyo biro rumo, (rumo chuth).
Ma Ruoth choko keyo mar jotich duto.
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye, gotieno ka piny oling' malich?
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye owadwa ne keyono madwong'maber.
Bende ipuonjo ji wach Nyasaye gi yorno maji nyalo winjo?
Mond' ichok cham maber chieng' keyono,
kawuono tim winjruok kod Ruoth Yesu.
Teche duto onego liel, mudho ni e piny kae;
Mudho maduong' nobed e piny ka Yesu pok obiro.
Nindo otero ji mang'eny, Gidagi wach Injili;
To wan waketo genowa kuom wach mar duogo Yesu.
Tachwa ni wachne madieri, Ok wa nalal kwaluwe
Kata masiche lworowa, ToYesu ok nowewa.
Tich maber onen pile, Mond' okwod wi jopinyni;
Wanayud gweth kuom tich maber Ka yie oriwo chunywa.
Yesu Kristo odwaro walem ndalowa duto te
Ochiwo Muche ni jogo Madwaro tekone.
Yesu Kristo odwaro walame Mondo wabed matek;
Miwa winj dwondi kawuono Kwatemo luwo ka.
Yesu Kristo odwaro walame nyaka chieng' giko piny;
Eka kobiro omowa Noterwa e polo.
Yesu Kristo odwaro walame, Ndalono chiegini;
Kwonde duto, e ru ler duto,
Mond' iland wach ni ji duto,
Ked Lweny maber ni Yesu Ruoth,
Gik man e piny kadho duto,
Nabed maler e nyim kom duong'.
Gen Yesu Kristo Gi wach Nyasaye.
A e nindo, Bedi ka jakedo;
Kaw okumba yie, Gi ogut Konyruok,
En gi migeno ma nyaka chieng',
kuom Yie, e dala me polo;
Ruoth, taya e yo mar polo.
dwond wend jo maler e polo.

title: In Migeno Chamo Mwandu Me Polo

lines: In migeno chamo mwandu me polo,
Tim kinda, to ndalo kadho piyo.
In migeno chamo mwandu me polo,
Duto mag piny kadho kendo rumo;
Waikre mar romo kod Ruoth gi mor.
Kata ok wang'eyo gi man e nyimwa,
Ka wariwo duondwa e wer mar locho,

title: Yaye Mad Abed Gi Yie Chutho

lines: Yaye mad abed gi yie chutho,
Yie ma ok dak obed gi ng'ur
Weche mag piny kik wuond chunya
Kuwe mar polo ma ni e chuny,
Sabato mari, Ruoth, Jogi ruako gi mor;
Kwarito winjo wach mari Chunywa mondo paki.
Wamor kuom ndaloni Ma isewalo, Ruoth; Wanaheri,
Jogi maler, gwedhgi! Bed kodwa kwalemo;
Ruoth, miwa mor kuom yueyoni, Kwarito chieng' maler.
Kidich piny korumo, Kwadar a thurwa ka;
Miwa dir kodi nyaka chieng' E dalani maler.
Chwo, to gi mon, gi nyithindo be;
Mondo wawuoth kuomgi e nyim ji;
Gik moko duto ma nie piny
To pok kethruok ni tho adier;
Kaka mor gi ler mar chieng'.
Wachokore gi mor tinde, kidira mar Nyasaye;
Gi mor bende wawer nyimi kwapako nyingi ka.
Ot kama jogi lamoi Onego bed maler
Chuny ji mosayi odi ni Ilosogi maber.
Muya Maler, Jakony mang'won, Dak ie kanisa ni;
Teche liel saa duto Te Komenyo e piny.
Nyasaye man malo, miwa mor Nyaka chunywa oyieng',
A waneni Wang' gi wang', Kwamor ma nyaka chieng'.
Wago ni Ruoth Nyasachwa erokamano ngang';
To oseritowa ma nyaka nend' okinyi.
Yesu ritwa gotienoni, kaka iseritowa chon.
To tichwa mar tinende koro oserumo;
Iritwa duto ka mang'won ka wanindo gotienoni.
Nyasaye, bedi Jakwadhwa, kaka nisingo chon
Nikech nitie e piny ka gik moko maricho Yaye!
Yesu, winjwa koro: warwa e gik maricho gi.
Polo to chido, Yesu bed koda;
In kendi inyalo teko mar Jachien;
E mudho be e chieng', bedi koda.
Tho to ok rach; to liel onyal ang'o?
An bend' aloyogi, ka In koda.
Chieng' tho inyisa kaka In nitho;
Ka piny ochido polo ek' orieny;
Chieng' cha noru, to mudho duto orum,
To gi dhano man e piny,

title: Yesu, In Ma Jahoch Mar Chuny

lines: Yesu, In ma Jahoch mar chuny,
To daluor tho da onge In.

To ka tich me piny ka rumo
Winji weche ma nondiki mag Nyasaye,
To an anaolnu gweth maduong' ng'ang',
Ma onge thuolo munyalo yie go."

Ng'a mowinjo dwond Ruoth, oneg' oyie;
Oland wachne mondo ji duto winje;
Wachne mond' odhiyo e pinje duto;
Ka ng'ato winjo, ka ng'ato winjo,

Ng'a mobiro piyo ok nodog nono;
Dhoranga polo yawore, Wayud kinde mar neno
Ler moa e msalap Yesu, Manyisowa herane.
Ni an, ni an, Oyawore ni an.
Rangano pod oyawore Ni joma richo duto,
Madongo gi matindo be, Magombo yudo warruok.
Watimuru kinda koro, Wayie ng'wono maduong'no;
Ka wasekalo aora, To wanawe msalaba;
Ruoth nomiwa ngima mak rum, Wanahere mochwere.
Ee, Yesu En e yo adier,

Ka en tem ma pinyni ok onyal golo,
Pim osiep Yesu gi mago machon,
Ka diher donje dala mar yueyo,
To an bende ma ok aler,
To an bende ma ok aler,
Ruoth Yesu, agombo bedo ng'ati chuth;
In mond' idag e chunya pile pile;
Gol kuoma maricho gi tim ma ok ler;
Luoka gi rembi mond' abedi mapoth.
Pwodha gi rembi, mond' abedi mapoth.
Ruoth Yesu, para gi e polo malo;
Luoka gi rembi mond' abedi mapoth.
Ruoth Yesu, akwayoi gi chuny mamuol,
Rembi mond' oguda kuom duto mak ler;
Luoka gi rembi mond' abedi mapoth.
Ruoth Yesu, aling' nyimi ka ageno,

Luoka gi rembi mond' abed mapoth.
En koluoka gi pi gi mach,
Ka chunya ler, ka chunya poth,

Rembe e moromo mana ji duto,
Enoyie ni mond' adonji e polo,

title: Yesu Luongi, We Ting'ni Mar Richo

lines: Yesu Luongi, we ting'ni mar richo;
Yie we paro kod sunga mar chunyi;
Bi bed maler kuom remb yadh Kalwari,
Yie mond' ibed matar moloyo pe,
Yie mondo itim tich Ruodhwa Yesu,
Yie mond' idend nyinge ndalo duto,

title: Nitie Ng'ama Noyie Tho Mondo Owara

lines: Nitie ng'ama noyie tho mondo owara,
Kendo yor kalwari noluwo kodhi tho,
Yesu nodhi e tho gi chandruok malich ngang',
En mang'won kendo ber, okecha pile ka
Aonge bura moro, an thuolo chutho
Ka awer gi dhoga kod wend pak e chunya,
In Kiol nikech chandruol e chunyi,
Ka luoro mar tho obwogo chunyi,
Mwandu mar piny en gi mokadho,
Mwandu mosiko ni kuom Ruoth Yesu.
Kwan gweth magi, hul achiel achiel,
Kwan gweth magi, ne tich mar Nyasaye;
Kwan gweth magi, hul achiel achiel,
Kendo iniwuor gi ma Ruoth notimo.
Koso in Jakristo man gi chuny mapek,
Par Yesu Jawarni, Chuny mapek noa,
Iniyud mor koro, kaa e piny ka.
Kineno jo moko man gi pith mag piny,
Par Yesu Jawarni, Ruoth polo malo.
Gen moloyo Kristo gi pok masiko.
Kendo e lwenje mond' ibed ng'at mager,
Wach mar miriambo lo gi wach maber;
Anayie Ruoth Yesu kende, asewinjo wach mare;
Onge gi manyalo loyo ng'ato mogeno Yesu.
Kethna duto awe kuome, enoluoka gi rembe;
Enorita nyaka chieng' ka notera ka Nyasaye.
Koro ok aluor gi moro, chunya koro genoi;
Kata yora timo mudho, Yesu ni lerna pile.
Chunya amiyo Ruoth Yesu, ringra bende amiye;
Ndalo duto enorita nyaka chieng'ma noduogi.
E piny ma keth ok nyal donjo,
Ka yo man e nyimi otimo mudho,
Nitie ler mogwedhi man kuom Ruoth Yesu,
Ne ler Yesu kaka orieny maler,
Gen Yesu kende nikech en machiegni.
Kata ok ing'eyo tiend ting'ni mapek,
Mosechandi e ngimani e piny ka;
Mond' iting' msalapi e chandruok duto,
Kendo igen Yesu ndalo duto te.
Dhi nyime kuom yie mondo ilo temruok,
King'eyo ka Jawar ni buti pile;
Kata ka lweny tek to kik chunyi oa,
Kata lweny ger chutho,  kata kuyo thoth,
Ruoth ni buti pile nomiyi teko,
ma nene obole e bur sibuoche;
Nyasaye ni lerna, koro ok aluor!
E mudho , e chieng', to En koda pile;
Nyasaye ni lerna, morna gi wenda;
Otelona pile e piny ka marach;
Nyasaye ni lerna, morna gi wenda;

Nyasaye ni lerna, e chandruok duto,
Kawuotho gi Yesu koro ok aluor.
Mudho onge chutho ka an kod Yesu;
saa ma wuodha norum e piny;

title: Kata Ka Abedo Gi Ngima Maber

lines: Kata ka abedo gi ngima maber,
Kuomi to anyalo bet gi kuwe.
Anyalo, bet gi kuwe e chunya.
Ne otho ni mond' ores chunya.
Ruoth Yesu, ru ndalono mar bironi,
Kwawuotho gi Ruodhwa, kuom ler manie wachne,
Yie nying Yesu, Bende lu e yore;
Mondo wayud mor kuome onego wawinje.
Ka wachandore ka, ka waneno malit,
Ok wanyal chwanyore, ok wanyal chandore,
Koro ok wanaluor ka wabedo kode,
Ka wahere kama, ka wawinjo chikne,
Kik wapar rem moro, Yesu oritowa,
Chieng' ka Yesu biro, eka wananene,
Kuyo ok wanane, kata chandruok moro,
Ruoth En E Jakwadha, orita maber;
Lum mang'ich omiya, oruaka e kunde;
Gima rach ok nyala ka Jakony ni buta.
Imiya gweth mang'eny ma onge kar giko;
Iolona mo mang'we ng'ar e wiya;
Mondo luwre koda nyak' achop iri ku;
Nalu yorno ma jo machon noluwo,
Nyak' adonji kanyo, pinyruodhi mar hera.
Weche madier, mag ngima winjiuru ji duto, mondo upargi;
Gin johawi momako chik duto, gin johawi;
Mit singruokne bedo kayiem; winjogi, luorogi, ok onyal konywa;
Jogo ma nodonji e dala, jo maler, maonge richo,
Jo mowar, mopwodhi, e remb Nyarombo,

title: Wuothi E Ler Mar Ruoth Nyasaye

lines: Wuothi e ler mar Ruoth Nyasaye, mamenyo wang'yori;
Muche maler, moa malo, nyalo riembo mudho.
Wuo...thi e ler...(wuothi e ler, wuoth e ler maber mar Nyasaye).
Wuo...thi e ler...Wuo..thi e ler, wuothi e lerno mar Nyasaye.
Wuothi e ler mar puonj Ruodhwa, moa kuom Wach Nyasaye;
Ler matelo ni nyithindo, moyie Weche Nyasaye.
Wuothi kata mudho olil modino wang'yori;
Mudho noringi e nyim ler, mar Ruoth ma nyaka chieng'.
Wuothi e ler eka ning'e kaka Ruoth oheri;
Wanabed gi winjruok maduong', moloyo mar piny ka.
Yesu En Osiep maber chutho, ka parruok mar piny hewo chunyi;
Enochangi chuny motuo, nochiw teko gi ng'wono,

(Yesu En Osiep, En Osiep maber ngang',)
Ee, Yesu En Osiep maber ngang',
Yesu En Osiepna moloyo; Omiya kuwe gi mor e chunya;

Ee, Yesu En Osiep maber ngang'.
Kata kuyo malit oyuda, kata kachopo e saa thona,
kibaji ok nogoya, nikech Jawar En koda,
Ee, Yesu En Osiep maber ngang'.
Ka wachokre e thurwa malo, Kachiel gi jogo ma notho chon,
Wanawer mamit kucha, kwadende ma nyaka chieng',
Owadwa kik iluor, Bedi gi chir pile;
Kata ka chunyi lit, Ka gigi kethore;
Kik chunyi ol, kik chunyi a, Nyasaye nomii kuwe.
Otieno to norum, Chieng' mar dimbruok nobi;
Masicheni duto nolal Ka Ruoth ofwenyore.
Gen hera mar Ruodhi, Onge motamo En;
Bedi pile e luetene, Noriti nyaka chieng'.
Yesu ni Jakwadhwa, to wan rombege;
En kowuoyo kodwa koro chunywa mor;
En kende Jakonywa, to wan nyithinde.
Mond' oluokwa chutho e kethruok duto;
Mago joge duto man gi Much Nyasaye.
Ka wagene pile nyaka chieng' watho,
Chieng' ka Yesu  duogo eka wanachier.
Ruoth, jiwa kuom saa mar lami.
To kik wamung' ni ji me piny,
To kak' abet ni an muofu,
Ka pod an ie piny ka,
Mor mar piny  to mana nono;
An mond' abed ka taya manyiso ler mari.
Weche piny ok nyal chanda ka In idak koda.
Arito mond' inyisa gi monego atim;
Ok danwang' mor e piny kae,
Pith gi duong' mar piny odok nono,
Kawito gik mantie e piny ka,
Asebayo mabor kodi Ruodha, koro abironi,
Adwaro mondo abed e ritni, koro abironi.
Koro adwogo Ruoth ee adwogo, Ruoth adwogo dala;
Koro adwogo, Ruoth ee adwogo, Ruoth adwogo dala.
Aol gi piny kod richo mogundho kor' adwogo dala;
Ayie Jawar norwaka e kunde kor' aduogo dala.
Ang'eyo Jawar nomiya yweyo kor' adwogo dala;
Adwaro keto chunya e lwete kor' aduogo dala.
Ayie tiyoni ka ng'ama jachan kor' adwogo dala;
Adwaro nwang'o ng'wono mar Jawar kor' adwogo dala.
Pakuru Ruoth, aneno Jawarna kor' adwogo dala;
Orito rwako jomolal ka an kor' adwogo dala.
Yuweyo ok niyud ngang' kata gweth malong'o,
Iseketo gigi te e kar Misango?
Inyalo yudo gweth mibedi gi kuwe chuth;
Ber iwuoth gi Ruodhi e ler manie wachne,
To niyuwe e yo maber mar Ruoth,
Nyak itim chik Ruodhi mond' ibed maler chuth,
Ok wanyal ng'eyo ngang' Gik ma Ruoth chiwonwa,
Oneg ochik chutho, Kendo wachiw duto misango.
Ng'a ma diwach hera mobiro oronwa,
Mit mar wuoyo kode noromwa waduto,
O Yesu, an adwaro Atini nyaka chieng'
Asayi bedi buta, Ruodha ma jakonya.
Ok analuor lwenj Satan ka In ibet buta;
Yo maber ok aweyo ka In itelona.
Mondo ang'e in koda, Pinyni oywayoa;
Wasika gi gilwora, Kendo gin e chunya;
O Yesu, bi, ikonya, Mondo alo Satan.
O Yesu, isewacho duto molu bang'i,
Ka ma intie e duong'ni Ginibedi bende.
To Yesu, an adwaro Atini nyaka chieng';
Asayi konya pile, Ruodha ma Jawarna.
Ka chunya lit, ka chunya yom,
Ka yamo nego ji e piny;
Ka tichna gik e pinywa ka,
Ndalo duto abed buti Nyasaye Wuora;
Achalo gi jawuoth e pinyni ka;
Kar yueyo ongena, ler onge be;
To adwaro siko buti Nyasaye Wuora,
Nyisa wang'yo mari, en e ma mond' alu;
Kochier a e liel ching' bironi,
Adonj ka ma Intie, Nyasaye Wuora;
Nayud mor mochwere e dalani maber,
Nabed buti pile, ma nyaka chieng'.

title: Ruoth Ni Koda E Yo Duto

lines: Ruoth ni koda e yo duto,
Ruoth ni koda e yo duto,
Ruoth ni koda e yo duto;
An anyap to in gi teko
Ka wuotho e geng aoch Jordan
An to kabedo bute, Onge gi manyalo luor.
Weche mabiro ira, Weche mamiya mor.
An to kabedo bute, Onge gi manyalo luor.
Piny ok onyalo teroa, Kata richo kethoa;
Kata aparo ndalo Ok analuor gimoro;
Kata ane masira, Chieng' anamor kucha.
An anadhi ka Yesu, En ma notho kuoma;
Piny pod otimo mudho Ka pod awuotho kae;
Piny to norum mapiyo, Eka nadhi kucha.
Ka Yesu telo, duto ber, ee, duto ber).
An gi kue ka an buti
In e kar bwok mar chunya
An gi kuwe ka in buta
Lweny mager e piny gi nam,
Makelo kibaji gi ngoro ni ji,
Yieno, ka ma Ruoth polo nindoe;
To Ruoth Yesu bi piyo, asayi;
Kuwe mari koro ni e chunya,
Eka danyal chopo ka maner cha,
Yesu obiro ka kendo, Yesu ma notho Kalwari;
Obiro omo jo moyie, Mondo gidhi polo.
Ee, obiro; ee, obiro; obiro machiegini.
Waneno tim mang'eny e piny Mapuonjowa wach birone;
Chieng'no obiro mana ru Ma wanadhi polo.
Ndalo mang'eny to lweny nitie; To pinje ok noyudi kuwe;
Nyaka Jawarwa wir' e piny, Mond' oterwa polo.
Eka e piny maber, manyien, Wanabedi ma nyaka chieng';
Ok wanachak waketh kendo, To wanamor pile.

title: Gin Weche Mamit Ma Jakristo Winjo

lines: Gin weche mamit ma Jakristo owinjo,
Ji duto maler ma notho kageno Ruoth,
Mowar a tung' piny duto nobedi kuro,
Kwarito gi kinda nyaka Ruodhwa nobi,
Jo maler duto rituru teko polo koro, Yiengni;
Mokuru techeu duto, kurito biro mar ruodhwa.
Obiro Yesu Ruodhwa; Obiro gi duong' mar polo;
Yesu biro e komduong'ne, Ruoth Yesu Kristo biro.
Landuru wach kwonde duto,Kunyiso ji wach mar warruok;
Kuom jathieth gi hera mare, kod teko mar weyo richo.
Pinje Ruodhi biro kadho; Pinyruodhe oduong' gilala;
Landuru wach nguono mare, Ka ndalogi pok okadho.
Ogend pinyni to lal nono, kamirima pong'o chunygi;
Kristo dwaro biro piyo, Mondo pinyruodhe ochungi.
Jo maricho to biuru, Mondo Kristo luoknu richo;
Returu, ukaw ng'wonone, ndalo koro chiegni rumo.
Landuru wachno e gode gi pap:
Nobi gi duong', Nyarombo ma notho;
Dho wedhe duto mond' owinj wachni:
Timbe mag piny nyiso ji duto wach;
Chieng'no maduong' to nobinwa piyo, mar biro Yesu;
Nobi ni mondo oter nyithinde e utgi malo.
Wach mar injili nolandre piyo ni dhoudi te;
Eka Ruoth Yesu Kristo noduogi, mi bu noyuagi .
Jopolo duto nokowe bende e boche polo;
Ruodhwa nobi tero jo makare kama tho onge.
Jo ma wahero to koro nindo; to wananere;
Ok wanayuagi e pinyruodh polo, wanamor kende.
Di po kobiro ka piny chido,
kata saa ma piny dwaro ru.
ka  jogo ma notho nigi mor,
Dong iikri romo ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro?
Dong iikri romo ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro?
Ikri mar romo ni Ruoth kobiro.
Ikri mar romo ni Ruoth kobiro.
Ni mond' une ka teche liel kobiro, kobiro;
Ni mond' une ka teche liel kobiro, kobiro.
Ikri mar romo ni Ruoth kobiro.
Duto wadhi warom ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro;
Duto wadhi warom ni Ruoth kobiro, kobiro.
Wanawer wende pak ka Ruoth biro.
En ma yand' otho ni ji;
Ma nodhur mathoth ka lum. Alleluya!
Di po ka nobed saa ma wang' chieng' opilre,
Kama ler oketho mudho mar otieno,
Ma Yesu nobi koa polo gi duong'ne
Ni mond' okaw joge e piny.
Koso odiechieng', koso ka piny oyuso,
koso odiewuor, Ma mudho chieng' noturnwa,
kod lerno malich; Ma norieny a e polo,
Malaika, To gi joge maler duto,
ka Malaika kowe e boche polo,
Nikech wan wakiya ndalo ma nobie,
Chieng'no kik powa, kendo bura kik lowa,
Yesu nobi kendo mondo oom joge;
Eka joge maler duto nobed kama Entie.
Un kik ukul wiu, to ng'iuru malo;
Piny noyiengni kendo, polo noa kare,
Mi jo mak ler nobed nade e ndalono maduong'?
Gionge kar ringo ka piny nobed malich,
Mirimb Nyasaye nonere ka ng'wono oserumo.
Wang'e maliel ka mach notiek jo maricho;
Onge lep ma nowach nyinge kayiem e ndalono;
Onge ng'a ma nonyier Jokristo e chieng'no;
Alam gi yuak mag jodong piny nobed kayiem chieng'no.
Keyo mar pinyni to koro chiegini;
Ruoth dwaro jokeyo ni mondo gibi,
Kendo gika chambe e puothe duto,
Mond' okan e deche ka Ruodhwa biro.
(Un jokeyo ret uru, ret uru, Kauru cham mar Ruodhwa, mar Ruodhwa;)
(Un jokeyo returu, returu, Ruoth chiegni biro.)
Ndalono mochwere, ma pi wang' onge,
To yamo mar richo dwaro keyo cham,
Kwatiyo gi hera to en tich mamit;
Ruodh hera moluongwa, wadhi wamak tich;
Cham ritowa koro to keyono duong'.

title: Chieng' Ma Bu Mar Nyasachwa Noyuagi

lines: Chieng' ma bu mar Nyasachwa noyuagi e ndalo giko,
Chieng'no e ma piny noyawre, nyaka chieng';
Chieng'no jo mowar nochokre e dho wadh aoch ngima.
Ka iluongo nying jo maler nabedie!
Ka iluongo nying jo maler, nabedie!
Chieng'no ma jo maler duto nowinji dwond bu kayuak.
Eka ginichokre kanyakla e dalano maler;
Ka iluongo nying jo maler, nabedie!
Watiuru ni Yesu gi kinda nyaka oduogi;
Eka chieng'no ma tichne duto norum e pinyni,
Ka iluongo nying jo maler, nabedie!
Ruodha, ok agomb moko, kata mwandu mar piny;
To adwaro ni mondo achopi e polo;
E kitapi mar Ngima, Yesu mond' inyisa,
Kata nyinga ondiki e kitapi kanyo.
Ondik nyinga koso, e kitapi maler?
E Kitapi mar Ngima, nyinga nitie koso?
An gi richo mang'eny ngang', machalo gi kuoyo;
Kata kamano, Ruodha, Rembi e moromo;
Nikech isesingo ni kata gibed makwar,
Ginibedi matar ngang', moloyo pe matar.
Yaye, dalano maber ngang', man gi udi marieny,
Kanyono jo modakie nigi nengni matar;
Nyinga bende ondiki, e kitapi koso?
Ji man gi lep kisera nomor,
Kama Ruoth nopog joge dhiyo korachich,
Dong iikri dong iikri ni ndalo nogo.
To lerne nobi ni jogo mohero Jawargi,
Ka nowach ni joricho "Auru ok ang'eu",

title: Koro Kawuono, Ruodhwa Man E Polo

lines: Koro kawuono, Ruodhwa man e polo,
Tich yandi ochaki kuom jo monindo;

Ka tichwa oserumo,                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ka wasetieko ng'wewa;

title: Ka Boche Polo Oyawo E Wi Gode

lines: E kar kom duong mar Nyasaye.
E dho aoch pi mar ngima,
Kaseruakora gi kido ma ok tow,
Ma Ruodhwa oiko ni joge maler;
Moyie mondo ayud kar bet e polo.
Dala wa man malo e polo,
(Dalawa dalawa dala man malo e polo);

title: Ndalo Duto Ma An E Piny

lines: Ndalo duto ma an e piny,
Ok wasiki e pinyni ma wantie;

title: Ji Noyud Mor Ka Tich Orumo

lines: Ji noyud mor ka tich orumo,
ka jo keyo biro gi cham
kod kwonde bet ma nyaka chieng',
Ka ma nitie pigno mar ngima,
Ka riyo loyi, bi ir Yesu,
Chieng' chopo polo gi joge duto,
Kulri nyim Yesu, gi kom mar Nyasaye,
Ji nobed gi chuny mar hera,
Orieny gi ler ma nyaka chieng',
Orieny gi ler ma nyaka chieng'.
Dala maber mar mor gi kuwe;
Da an gi buomb winyo koro,
E piny ka mond' atim chikne,
to Wan wadhi ka piny moloyo;
Nawe ting'na duto piny kadhi polo;
Eka nane ler achien kadhi polo;
Ka ler mar polo rieny komenyo wang' yora,
Nawer ng'wono mar Jawar kadhi polo;
Kachungo e nyime, anapake gi mor,
Asewinjo kuom piny man mabor loka nam,
En kar dak maber mar jo mo war;
Yesu e moloso udi mag dalano,
En piny ma ok wanabed moti.
E dalano maber ma ok wanalalie,
Wanapak Ruoth Yesu e piny Ruoth mochwere,
Yuak gi tem norum chuth, wanawer gi jogo,
En kar yuweyo maber bang' chandruok duto.
En piny ma nosingi chon ni jogo maler.
Kama cham kod olembe nomi chunywa mor.
En piny maber, en piny maber;
En piny maber, en piny maber,
En piny maber, en piny maber ngang'.
Wanawinj thumbe mayuak mamit e polo;
Ka jomalaika maler nower gi mor,
Osiepe ma jowuodha koro chiegni wuok,
Nikech yie nigi teko mar fwenyo weche;
Piny chandruokni kod gik mak ne,
Ka ma pi, wang' noywe duto.
E loka nam e nam mogingore,
E loka nam e dho wadh kuwe
E loka nam kar kuwe gi mor
E dho wath marieny, dho nam dhahabu,
E dala Wuonwa e pinyno mar mor.
To ka ndalo mad wuoth norum,

title: Ase Chop' E Piny Mar Mwandu

lines: Ase chop' e piny mar mwandu,
O piny maber, piny maber ngang',
Ka wang'a kadho e wi nam'
Ni kech ma e polo maler.
ma tikne a e yadh ngima,
Ma thiepege ok nyal nur ngang',
Nyasaye nomiyo Adam Jakony e puoth Eden;
To pod oyie ni dhano Mond' okonyre kama.
Nikech wachni maduong' to dichwo nowe jonyuol;
Ni mond' odag gi chiege; Ginibedi kachiel.
Chwo mondo giher mondgi gi hera ma kama.
Kanisa to owinjo Weche duto mag Ruoth;
Ka mon winjo chwogi, Winjruok nitie maber.
Konyruok moro to onge mak In mibet kodwa.
Riw chunygi chutho koro gi hera mosiko.
Kumako yo me nyimu mad Nyasaye ogwedhu;
Morne gi kuwe madieri obed kodu pile.
To mor gi kuwe nobed e chunywa,
Okuwe mos kanyo e i liel,
Nindo kuom Yesu! Ma ber ngang';

title: Ruodha Dak Ipogna Kuon Mar Ngima

lines: Ka wiya wil kendo ka aruenyo,
Chieng' moro wanawer wer e polo,
mond' otho ni ji me piny,

title: Luetega Noti Tich Mar Ruoth Yesu

lines: Luetega noti tich mar Ruoth Yesu,
Ka ne gipako Yesu Ruodh polo;
gi jo mowar, eka wanamor ngang';
To di po kaol e yo;

title: Nysaye Oneno Ka Winyo Odwaro Gore Piny
Ahero Ahinya Mar Chopo E Skul Mar Sabato

lines: Ee, nochweyo duto kuom wachne kende.
Yien, gi lum, gi chiembwa, rech man nie nam,
Sulwe to gi dwe be marieny gotieno.
En onyalo hingo wach Nyasaye adier.
Un nyithindo, ruak Yesu e chunyu,
Un nyithindo, ruak Yesu e chunyu,

title: Bedo Gi Yesu E Dala, Mano Mor Maduong'

lines: Ka Yesu ni e chuny wuoro,
Ka Yesu ni e chuny wuoro,
Ka Yesu ni e chuny miyo,
Ka Yesu ni e chuny miyo,
Ne litna ka richona nokelo tho,
Kendo kanaywak e bugo mar richo;
Ruoth nowinja gi e bugo matutno,
Ok naluor podho kasiko e lwete,
Nagen kuom ng'uonone nyaka ayud locho.
Nomiya wer mamit ne en wer mar pak,
Chunya nigi ilo amor an thuolo,
Anawer wend warruok kuonde duto te,
Nyaka ji mang'eny noyie kuom Nyasaye.
Ka in gi geno kuome chutho,
Chuny ma en go opong' kod ng'uono,
En kama mor gi kwe nitie,
Gik moko te ma lueti noloso.
Ka awuotho e bunge to awinjo,
Ka abedo e gode mabor chutho,
Mondo otho en wach miwuoro ngang';
E wi yadhno noting'o kethna duto,
Ka Kristo nobi gi teko gi duong'ne,
Nakulra e nyime ka amiye duong',
Med telona, mudho olil an mabor gi dala;
Med telona ok anyal neno mabor moloyo,
Ne an mabor ne ok ageno kuomi, Koro telna;
Ne ahero yiero yora awuon, koro telna;
Chunya kod ringruok ne kedo lweny mager,
Pod notelna kuom chandruok gi masiche moluora ndalo duto;
Bang'e namor kod jomalaika masegombo neno ndalo duto.
Ng'ato nodonj e ranga lulu e chieng'no,
E chieng'no mond' one duong'no maritowa.
In koso an? In koso an?
Ng'at ma nolu yo mar dhahabu,
In koso an? In Koso an?
Ng'at ma nomor ka oselocho, e chieng'no,
E chieng'no, noyud osimbo kod pak kuom Ruoth;
In koso an? In koso an?
Ng'at manone Ruodhwa man gi duong',
In Koso an? In koso an?
Ng'at manower wendno mar locho, e chieng'no,
E chieng'no, noriwre e wend jomosewar;
In koso an? In koso an?
Ng'at manochung' e dho nam rang'i,
In koso an? In koso an?
Wer mar mor kod wend locho, Alleluya!
Polo wer be piny duoko, Alleluya!
Ere lit ma tho kelo? Alleluya!
Ere loch ma liel nigo? Alleluya!
Tho to ok nyal geng'e ngang', Alleluya!

title: Kik Chunyi A Kat' E Chandruok

lines: Kik chunyi a kat' e chandruok,
Bang' loyo twech sand kod mach be;
Ywaya iri, iri, iri, Ruoth maber,
Ywaya iri, iri, iri, Ruoth maber,
Kata ka, kata ku, analu bang'e;

title: An Achamo Kuon Mar Ngima Adier

lines: An achamo kuon mar ngima adier,
To amodho pi mar Yesu owuon;
